      Classes in transforma.qb2_user_app.rosmsg that implement RosBridgeListener 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  InspectionResult
      This is a singleton class of inspection result that only creates itself when the inspection starts It's created to store relevant numbers relating to inspection result. Check whether the inspectionMode result attribute is null or not to determine whether there is an ongoing inspection. Making inspectionResult null pointer is necessary when an inspection finishes. Adding & Removing RosBridgeListener is necessary to prevent error occuring
